00:03:37.910 --> 00:03:48.310
Let's Go!

00:03:48.310 --> 00:03:53.770
Pablo Castaño is a digital artist from Argentina
that combines 3D fractals and photographs

00:03:53.770 --> 00:03:56.220
to give scale to his landscapes.

00:03:56.220 --> 00:04:01.580
Oliver Smith moved from England to Thailand
where he built a bar and hostel based on Jenga

00:04:01.580 --> 00:04:02.800
blocks.

00:04:02.800 --> 00:04:06.160
Russ sculpts car bodies out of inexpensive
potters clay.

00:04:06.160 --> 00:04:11.890
He builds and drives his own exotic muscle
cars and also teaches others his awesome techniques.

00:04:11.890 --> 00:04:17.370
Vitaliy is a graphic designer from Portugal
who created a series of abstract wallpapers

00:04:17.370 --> 00:04:22.710
depicting seven U.S. states - including California,
Florida and New York.

00:04:22.710 --> 00:04:31.569
Here’s ALfiux with the track Nebula from
