00:04:31.569 --> 00:04:39.370
Edvinas Petrauskas painstakingly recreated
the cabin from Breaking Bad as a playable

00:04:39.370 --> 00:04:42.150
real-time environment for the Oculus Rift.

00:04:42.150 --> 00:04:47.349
Joe builds everything from an iPhone stand
and tissue box cover to an outdoor sand and

00:04:47.349 --> 00:04:50.200
